{
  "id": "63a7004c4b47b1001ea59c05",
  "title": "権利と正しさ",
  "created": 1671888974,
  "updated": 1671889415,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "63a7004eaff09e0000840073",
      "text": "権利と正しさ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671888974,
      "updated": 1671888979
    },
    {
      "id": "63a70076aff09e0000840086",
      "text": "権利とは何か",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671889014,
      "updated": 1671889014
    },
    {
      "id": "63a7007caff09e0000840087",
      "text": " >That which complies with justice, law or reason. ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671889021,
      "updated": 1671889033
    },
    {
      "id": "63a7007daff09e0000840088",
      "text": "  > We're on the side of right in this contest.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671889021,
      "updated": 1671889023
    },
    {
      "id": "63a7007daff09e0000840089",
      "text": " > A legal, just or moral entitlement.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671889021,
      "updated": 1671889023
    },
    {
      "id": "63a7007daff09e000084008a",
      "text": "  > You have no right to go through my personal diary.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671889021,
      "updated": 1671889023
    },
    {
      "id": "63a7007daff09e000084008b",
      "text": "　そもそも英語では[right]って言葉に「[正義]・[正しさ]」という意味と「[権利]」という意味が重なってる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671889021,
      "updated": 1671889117
    },
    {
      "id": "63a700bdaff09e000084008c",
      "text": "\t\t概念を適切に分割できてなさそうな気がする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671889086,
      "updated": 1671889160
    },
    {
      "id": "63a700bdaff09e000084008d",
      "text": "\t　正義に適ってるものが「正しさ」で、法に適ってるものが「権利」という考え方なのかなぁ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671889086,
      "updated": 1671889167
    },
    {
      "id": "63a700f4aff09e0000840090",
      "text": "　>日本語の「権利」という言葉には、「正しい」という意味は含まれていない。逆に、「権」という言葉は「[力]」([power])という意味を含んでいるから、「権利」は、自分の利益を力ずくでおし通すといったニュアンスをもつ。だから、「権利ばかりを主張するのは問題だ」といわれたりする。しかし、この命題の「権利」を“right”におきかえてみれば、それが成り立ちえない命題であることがすぐにわかる。「right(正しいこと)ばかりを主張する」のに何の問題もないはずだからである。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671889140,
      "updated": 1671889198
    },
    {
      "id": "63a70118aff09e0000840091",
      "text": "　 https://www.pref.tottori.lg.jp/secure/316971/1point-2.pdf",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671889177,
      "updated": 1671889177
    },
    {
      "id": "63a70118aff09e0000840092",
      "text": "　 この切り口は面白い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671889177,
      "updated": 1671889186
    },
    {
      "id": "63a70118aff09e0000840093",
      "text": "　　権利の権の字は権力、実権、権威、権益、特権、権限…などに使われる字",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671889177,
      "updated": 1671889177
    },
    {
      "id": "63a7013daff09e00009b6bcd",
      "text": "　ちなみに中国語でも同じ字(簡体字)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671889214,
      "updated": 1671889248
    },
    {
      "id": "63a70160aff09e00009b6bce",
      "text": "　ヨーロッパと東アジアで概念が食い違ってる可能性もあるな",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671889248,
      "updated": 1671889307
    },
    {
      "id": "63a70122aff09e0000840094",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671889187,
      "updated": 1671889187
    },
    {
      "id": "63a7005aaff09e0000840077",
      "text": "from [/villagepump/権利と正しさ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671888987,
      "updated": 1671889415
    },
    {
      "id": "63a70055aff09e0000840075",
      "text": "[権利]と[正しさ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671888982,
      "updated": 1671888985
    },
